# MDDatetimePickerComponent
The `MDDatetimePickerComponent` interface represents an HTML `<md-datetime-picker>` element, DateTime Picker Component

## Constructor
{{description}}

## Inheritance
`MDSheetComponent`

## Events
Listen to these events using `addEventListener()`, or by assigning an event listener to the `@onEventName` property of this interface.

Name | Description
--- | ---
`onDatetimePickerIconButtonClick` | Fired when an icon button in the picker is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerButtonClick` | Fired when a button in the picker is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerIconButtonPrevClick` | Fired when the previous icon button is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerIconButtonNextClick` | Fired when the next icon button is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerButtonLabelClick` | Fired when the label button is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerButtonCancelClick` | Fired when the cancel button is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerButtonOkClick` | Fired when the OK button is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerYearItemClick` | Fired when a year item is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerMonthItemClick` | Fired when a month item is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerDayItemClick` | Fired when a day item is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerHourItemClick` | Fired when an hour item is clicked.
`onDatetimePickerSelection` | Fired when a date selection is made.
`onDatetimePickerMinuteItemClick` | Fired when a minute item is clicked.

